Source: rdk-logger
Version: 2.4.0
Upstream-URL: https://github.com/rdkcentral/rdk_logger.git
Upstream-Ref: v2.4.0
Build-Depends: liblog4c-dev

Package: librdk-logger
Section: libs
Priority: optional
Depends: libc6, liblog4c3
Description: RDK Logger - Runtime library
 RDK Logger is a general-purpose logging mechanism for RDK components.
 It supports multiple log levels and modules, with log levels configured
 via a configuration file (debug.ini). Each module can have its own log
 level, and these can be changed at runtime using the provided CLI utility.
 .
 This package contains the runtime library and configuration files.

Package: librdk-logger-dev
Section: libdevel
Priority: optional
Depends: librdk-logger (= ${version})
Description: RDK Logger - Development files
 RDK Logger is a general-purpose logging mechanism for RDK components.
 .
 This package contains the development headers and static libraries.

Package: rdk-logger-utils
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Depends: libc6, librdk-logger (= ${version})
Description: RDK Logger - Utilities
 RDK Logger is a general-purpose logging mechanism for RDK components.
 .
 This package contains the rdklogctrl and rdklogmilestone utilities
 for runtime control of logging levels.
